& [LaneResults] is the first-pass outcome table
  + [bsd] is highest initial solution-potential lane
    = strongest_meaning: source collapse/growth language maps best to analytic order, Mordell-Weil rank, height/regulator measurement, and higher-rank source/measurement pairings
    = best_tooling: Math Bridge Map, Rank Bridge Case Splitter, Higher Rank Frontier Matrix, Source Measurement Pairing Table, Dimension Closure Checklist
    = open_lock: higher-rank independence, nondegenerate height/regulator pairing, sufficient source count, and upper-bound control outside special settings
    = proof_status: no BSD proof found
  + [navier_stokes] is dynamic-control lane
    = strongest_meaning: surface tension/resonance anchors map to geometric depletion, vorticity-direction coherence, alignment, and anti-concentration criteria
    = best_tooling: Anti-Blowup Gate Matrix and Depletion Propagation Checklist
    = open_lock: no general dynamic propagation of depletion/alignment strong enough to close a critical continuation criterion for arbitrary smooth data
    = proof_status: no Navier-Stokes proof found
  + [hodge] is realization lane
    = strongest_meaning: memory anchors map to rational Hodge classes only after variant boundaries are enforced
    = best_tooling: Anchor Realization Gate, Variant Boundary Map, Cycle Realization Mechanism Table
    = open_lock: rational higher-codimension algebraic cycle construction/realization remains the hard step
    = proof_status: no Hodge proof found
  + [p_vs_np] is formal-target lane
    = strongest_meaning: structure-over-enumeration maps best to CSP/SAT target selection, tractable-subclass insight, and heuristic search boundaries
    = best_tooling: Complexity Target Gate, Target Selection Table, CSP Coherence Translation Gate, Toy CSP Coherence Model
    = open_lock: no source-derived polynomial-time complete solver for SAT, 3-SAT, or an NP-complete CSP family
    = proof_status: no P vs NP proof found
  + [yang_mills] is construction-gap lane
    = strongest_meaning: sealed curvature maps only to partial intuition for confinement, exponential decay, or localization after construction exists
    = best_tooling: Existence-Gap Separation Gate and Construction Route Checklist
    = open_lock: no continuum construction, no gauge-invariant observable construction, no OS reconstruction, and no uniform gap-transfer theorem
    = proof_status: no Yang-Mills proof found
  + [poincare] is solved-problem boundary lane
    = strongest_meaning: symbolic Ricci flow maps to project narrative or future computational-cognition model, not topology proof
    = best_tooling: Solved-Problem Authority Gate and Symbolic Ricci Flow Model Boundary
    = open_lock: define state space, geometry, update rule, invariant, convergence metric, failure modes, and validation if pursuing the model
    = proof_status: accepted proof remains Perelman/Hamilton Ricci-flow lineage; no new proof needed or claimed

